{"tid":2343842,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"疫苗副作用成疑更怕國產  九成醫護市民表明唔打","createTime":"2020-12-28T08:46:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-28T12:56:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b9cb8016bfcf100a42128659be2f6c3fd3a7d4f2","tid":2343842,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T08:46:07.000Z","msg":"#香港新冠疫苗 #疫苗副作用 #Appledaily<br />\n<br />\n疫苗副作用成疑更怕國產 <br />\n九成醫護市民表明唔打 <br />\n蘋果日報 Apple Daily<br />\n&mdash;原刊日期： 20201226<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RQHE0GK-wEY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRQHE0GK-wEY&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjd4L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=be756efa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RQHE0GK-wEY</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蘋果動新聞 HK Apple Daily<br />\n1.77M subscribers<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】武漢肺炎影響全球已整年，香港政府月中宣佈，已採購三款疫苗供香港市民免費接種，其中來自中國的疫苗最快下月抵港。本報調查發現，近九成一般公眾及九成九受訪醫護人員表明不會馬上接種疫苗，主要擔心疫苗副作用，亦對政府揀選的藥廠無信心。有傳染病專科醫生指出，武肺疫苗研究時間短，功效及副作用等仍有待研究及觀察，公眾可多了解及諮詢家庭醫生意見，但強調長遠仍有必要接種。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201...&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjd4L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=15364151\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201...&h=4dcba329\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201...</a><br />\n<br />\n蘋果日報 ： <a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjd4L97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=509fe996\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com&h=bbd68420\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com</a><br />\n即 like 蘋果 fb  ： <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextm